---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Design Framework | StartMicrolearning" description="Master the MICRO framework for effective microlearning design. Learn systematic approaches to content strategy, instructional design patterns, and user experience optimization.">
  <div class="design-framework-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">Design Framework</h1>
      <p class="page-description">
        Master the MICRO methodology for creating effective microlearning experiences
      </p>
      <hr class="page-rule" />
    </header>

    <div class="framework-overview">
      <h2>The MICRO Framework</h2>
      <p class="framework-intro">
        Our systematic approach to microlearning design ensures every learning experience 
        drives measurable performance outcomes. Each component builds upon the others to 
        create engaging, effective learning moments.
      </p>
      
      <div class="micro-components">
        <div class="micro-component">
          <div class="component-header">
            <div class="micro-letter">M</div>
            <h3>Motivation</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="component-content">
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Foster intrinsic and extrinsic motivation through relevance, autonomy, and clear value</p>
            <h4>Key Strategies:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Apply Self-Determination Theory principles (autonomy, competence, relatedness)</li>
              <li>Connect learning to personal and professional goals</li>
              <li>Use compelling scenarios and real-world relevance</li>
              <li>Provide choice and control in learning paths</li>
              <li>Create curiosity gaps and meaningful challenges</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="example-box">
              <h5>Example:</h5>
              <p>"Choose your learning path: Customer service scenarios, email templates, or conflict resolution strategies - all designed to help you handle difficult situations with confidence."</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="micro-component">
          <div class="component-header">
            <div class="micro-letter">I</div>
            <h3>Interaction</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="component-content">
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Design engaging activities for active participation</p>
            <h4>Key Strategies:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Click-and-reveal interactions</li>
              <li>Drag-and-drop exercises</li>
              <li>Branching scenarios with choices</li>
              <li>Quick polls and knowledge checks</li>
              <li>Gamified elements and progress tracking</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="example-box">
              <h5>Example:</h5>
              <p>Interactive decision tree where learners choose responses and see immediate consequences.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="micro-component">
          <div class="component-header">
            <div class="micro-letter">C</div>
            <h3>Challenge</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="component-content">
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Provide practice and problem-solving opportunities</p>
            <h4>Key Strategies:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Realistic workplace scenarios</li>
              <li>Progressive difficulty levels</li>
              <li>Safe-to-fail practice environments</li>
              <li>Immediate feedback on performance</li>
              <li>Multiple attempts with guidance</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="example-box">
              <h5>Example:</h5>
              <p>Simulation where learners practice difficult conversations with virtual colleagues.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="micro-component">
          <div class="component-header">
            <div class="micro-letter">R</div>
            <h3>Retention</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="component-content">
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Enhance memory and long-term knowledge reinforcement</p>
            <h4>Key Strategies:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Spaced repetition scheduling</li>
              <li>Retrieval practice exercises</li>
              <li>Visual memory aids and mnemonics</li>
              <li>Connection to prior knowledge</li>
              <li>Summary and key takeaway reinforcement</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="example-box">
              <h5>Example:</h5>
              <p>Follow-up micro-modules delivered 3 days, 1 week, and 1 month later for reinforcement.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="micro-component">
          <div class="component-header">
            <div class="micro-letter">O</div>
            <h3>Outcomes</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="component-content">
            <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Measure impact on performance and business results</p>
            <h4>Key Strategies:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Clear, measurable learning objectives</li>
              <li>Performance-based assessments</li>
              <li>Behavior change tracking</li>
              <li>Business impact metrics</li>
              <li>Continuous improvement feedback loops</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="example-box">
              <h5>Example:</h5>
              <p>Track customer satisfaction scores before and after customer service microlearning deployment.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="content-strategy" id="content-strategy">
      <h2>Content Strategy & Planning</h2>
      <p>
        Effective microlearning starts with strategic content planning that aligns 
        with business objectives and learner needs.
      </p>
      
      <div class="strategy-sections">
        <div class="strategy-section">
          <h3>Learning Objectives for Microlearning</h3>
          <p>Microlearning objectives should be:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Specific:</strong> Target one clear skill or knowledge area</li>
            <li><strong>Actionable:</strong> Enable immediate application</li>
            <li><strong>Measurable:</strong> Include observable behaviors</li>
            <li><strong>Relevant:</strong> Connect to real work challenges</li>
            <li><strong>Time-bound:</strong> Achievable in 2-10 minutes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="strategy-section">
          <h3>Content Audit & Chunking</h3>
          <p>Transform existing training materials:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Identify core concepts and supporting details</li>
            <li>Break complex topics into logical sequences</li>
            <li>Remove non-essential information</li>
            <li>Create standalone learning moments</li>
            <li>Ensure each chunk has clear value</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="strategy-section">
          <h3>Just-in-Time Learning Design</h3>
          <p>Design for moment-of-need delivery:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Map learning to workflow touchpoints</li>
            <li>Create searchable, tagged content</li>
            <li>Design for mobile consumption</li>
            <li>Enable quick access and exit</li>
            <li>Provide immediate applicability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="design-patterns">
      <h2>Instructional Design Patterns</h2>
      <p>
        Proven templates and patterns for creating engaging microlearning experiences.
      </p>
      
      <div class="pattern-grid">
        <div class="pattern-card">
          <h3>Scenario-Based Learning</h3>
          <p>Present realistic workplace situations that require decision-making and problem-solving.</p>
          <div class="pattern-structure">
            <h4>Structure:</h4>
            <ol>
              <li>Set the scene (context)</li>
              <li>Present the challenge</li>
              <li>Offer choices</li>
              <li>Show consequences</li>
              <li>Provide guidance</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pattern-card">
          <h3>Progressive Disclosure</h3>
          <p>Reveal information gradually to prevent cognitive overload and maintain engagement.</p>
          <div class="pattern-structure">
            <h4>Structure:</h4>
            <ol>
              <li>Start with overview</li>
              <li>Click to reveal details</li>
              <li>Layer additional context</li>
              <li>Provide deep-dive options</li>
              <li>Summarize key points</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pattern-card">
          <h3>Challenge-Solution</h3>
          <p>Present problems followed by step-by-step solutions with practice opportunities.</p>
          <div class="pattern-structure">
            <h4>Structure:</h4>
            <ol>
              <li>Present the problem</li>
              <li>Guide through solution</li>
              <li>Provide practice scenario</li>
              <li>Give feedback</li>
              <li>Offer additional resources</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pattern-card">
          <h3>Comparison & Contrast</h3>
          <p>Help learners understand differences between concepts, approaches, or procedures.</p>
          <div class="pattern-structure">
            <h4>Structure:</h4>
            <ol>
              <li>Introduce concepts</li>
              <li>Show side-by-side comparison</li>
              <li>Highlight key differences</li>
              <li>Provide decision criteria</li>
              <li>Test understanding</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="next-steps-section">
      <h2>Ready to Apply the Framework?</h2>
      <p>
        Now that you understand the MICRO framework, it's time to put it into practice.
      </p>
      
      <div class="next-actions">
        <div class="action-card">
          <h3>Start Developing</h3>
          <p>Learn about tools and technologies for creating microlearning content.</p>
          <a href="/development-tools" class="action-link">Development Tools →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="action-card">
          <h3>Plan Implementation</h3>
          <p>Get strategies for deploying microlearning in your organization.</p>
          <a href="/implementation" class="action-link">Implementation Guide →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="action-card">
          <h3>Measure Success</h3>
          <p>Discover how to track and optimize your microlearning initiatives.</p>
          <a href="/measurement" class="action-link">Measurement & Analytics →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .design-framework-page {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-primary);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .page-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .page-rule {
    height: 4px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    border: none;
    width: 120px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .framework-overview {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 10);
  }

  .framework-overview h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .framework-intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto calc(var(--grid-unit) * 6);
  }

  .micro-components {
    display: grid;
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .micro-component {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .micro-component:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .component-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .micro-letter {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading-primary);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .component-header h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .component-content p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
  }

  .component-content h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2) 0 calc(var(--grid-unit));
  }

  .component-content h5 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2);
  }

  .component-content ul {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
    padding-left: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .component-content li {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .example-box {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
  }

  .example-box p {
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .content-strategy,
  .design-patterns,
  .next-steps-section {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 8);
  }

  .content-strategy h2,
  .design-patterns h2,
  .next-steps-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .strategy-sections {
    display: grid;
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .strategy-section {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent);
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .strategy-section h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
  }

  .pattern-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .pattern-card {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .pattern-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .pattern-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
  }

  .pattern-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
  }

  .pattern-structure h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
  }

  .pattern-structure ol {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
  }

  .pattern-structure li {
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) / 2);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .next-actions {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    margin-top: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 4);
  }

  .action-card {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 3);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .action-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .action-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit));
  }

  .action-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: calc(var(--grid-unit) * 2);
  }

  .action-link {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-secondary);
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .action-link:hover,
  .action-link:focus {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .component-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .pattern-grid,
    .next-actions {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>